                What are common job tasks for individuals working in the Medical Lab Assistant / Technician field?
            </h2>
            <p class="contentp">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cog blueGoldBorderSM f15"></span>&nbsp;Prepare reagents and solution, in addition to processing specimens.
                <br /><hr class="hrp">
